               <interp inst="t17481012-17" type="uri" value="sessionsPapers/17481012"></interp>
               <interp inst="t17481012-17" type="date" value="17481012"></interp>
               <join result="criminalCharge" id="t17481012-17-off95-c132" targOrder="Y" targets="t17481012-17-defend163 t17481012-17-off95 t17481012-17-verdict99"></join>
         
               <p>495. 
               
                  <persName id="t17481012-17-defend163" type="defendantName">
                     Mary 
                     Chambers 
                  <interp inst="t17481012-17-defend163" type="surname" value="Chambers"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17481012-17-defend163" type="given" value="Mary"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17481012-17-defend163" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
            , of <placeName id="t17481012-17-defloc94">St. Michael Cornhill</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17481012-17-defloc94" type="placeName" value="St. Michael Cornhill"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17481012-17-defloc94" type="type" value="defendantHome"></interp>
                  <join result="persNamePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17481012-17-defend163 t17481012-17-defloc94"></join>, was indicted for <rs id="t17481012-17-off95" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17481012-17-off95" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17481012-17-off95" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing a pair of scissars value 12 d. and two dozen of gown eyes, value 2 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17481012-17-victim165" type="victimName">
                     Henry 
                     Oldham 
                  <interp inst="t17481012-17-victim165" type="surname" value="Oldham"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17481012-17-victim165" type="given" value="Henry"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17481012-17-victim165" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17481012-17-off95 t17481012-17-victim165"></join>
                  </persName>
                
            , <rs id="t17481012-17-cd96" type="crimeDate">September 8</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17481012-17-off95 t17481012-17-cd96"></join>.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17481012-17-person166">
                  James 
                  Cook 
               <interp inst="t17481012-17-person166" type="surname" value="Cook"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17481012-17-person166" type="given" value="James"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17481012-17-person166" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am apprentice to Mr. 
               <persName id="t17481012-17-person167">
                  Henry 
                  Oldham 
               <interp inst="t17481012-17-person167" type="surname" value="Oldham"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17481012-17-person167" type="given" value="Henry"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17481012-17-person167" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             , <placeName id="t17481012-17-crimeloc97">
                     <rs id="t17481012-17-viclabel98" type="occupation">a hardware shop</rs>
                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17481012-17-victim165 t17481012-17-viclabel98"></join>, opposite to St. Michaell, in Cornhill</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17481012-17-crimeloc97" type="placeName" value="a hardware shop, opposite to St. Michaell, in Cornhill"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17481012-17-crimeloc97" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17481012-17-off95 t17481012-17-crimeloc97"></join>.</p>
               <p>Q. Do you know the prisoner?</p>
               <p>Cook. Yes; that woman and another woman came into my master's shop on the eighth or ninth of September; the prisoner came in and asked for a pair of snuffers, and she took a pair of scissars.</p>
               <p>Q. Did you see her take the scissars?</p>
               <p>Cook. Yes; I opened a paper of snuffers, and asked her a shilling, she said they were not good enough; and as I was looking down, I saw her take a paper of gown eyes about a gross; and while I was opening the snuffers, a gentleman came in, and she would have gone off, and said the snuffers were not worth 2 d. the other woman went out of the shop, and the prisoner after her: I went after the prisoner about half a dozen yards, and asked her if she had not got a paper out of the shop; she denied it, I brought her into our shop again, and she stood close by the side of the counter, and hid the snuffers under a paper, and the gross of gown eyes I saw her throw behind the counter: at twelve o'clock she was sent to the counter, and between three and four to Guild Hall, and she said she was innocent.</p>
               <p>Q. Did you take up the paper and put into her hand, that you took up from behind the counter , that you say she threw down?</p>
               <p>Cook. I took up the paper which she threw be hind the computer.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17481012-17-verdict99" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17481012-17-verdict99" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17481012-17-verdict99" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder1s"></interp>
               Guilty 10 d
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17481012-17-punish100" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17481012-17-punish100" type="punishmentCategory" value="corporal"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17481012-17-punish100" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="whipping"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17481012-17-defend163 t17481012-17-punish100"></join>
               
                     <note>[Whipping. See summary.]</note>
               
                  </rs>
               </p>
            </div1>
